How about posting to a signup thread in the events section of the boards. Recruit a large number of people or guilds that would be willing to assist you with the Ragefire kill. When Ragefire pops next, you will have an even larger number of volunteers to call in at a moment's notice for support. I'm sure there are hundreds who post here who would be willing to assist you. Some guild leaders might even be willing to sign up the entire guild for assistance.<br>
